ApplicationSubmissionInfoGrp.RestrictionsOnAwardsTxt: MUST BE A FOUNDER THAT IS A WOMAN OR NON-BINARY PERSON, FOUNDER MUST OWN 51% OR GREATER STAKE IN THE BUSINESS AS OF THE APPLICATION DUE DATE, APPLICANT MUST BE A LEGAL RESIDENT AND CITIZEN OF THE UNITED STATES, APPLICANT MUST BE 21 YEARS OR OLDER AS OF APPLICATION DUE DATE, MUST HAVE A TEAM THAT IS MADE UP OF 50% OR MORE WOMEN, FEMME, OR NON-BINARY PEOPLE, PROFICIENT IN ENGLISH. BUSINESS CRITERIA: BUSINESS MUST BE INCORPORATED, LOCATED, AND OPERATE IN THE US, CONSUMER-BASED PRODUCTS / BUSINESS (DIRECT TO CONSUMER, BUSINESS TO BUSINESS), 2021 GROSS REVENUE OF $75K - $2M USD, BUSINESS MUST NOT HAVE PREVIOUSLY RAISED FUNDING FROM VENTURE CAPITAL FIRMS, FOR-PROFIT COMPANIES IN BUSINESS SINCE OR PRIOR TO JANUARY 1, 2020, STAFF SIZE BETWEEN 2-30 EMPLOYEES (FULL-TIME, PART-TIME, INDEPENDENT CONTRACTORS). NOT ELIGIBLE: LOCATIONS OWNED BY PUBLICLY-TRADED CORPORATIONS DO NOT QUALIFY, NONPROFIT ORGANIZATIONS AND SUBSIDARY BUSINESSES OR FRANCHISEES DO NOT QUALIFY. AWARDS WILL BE $10,000.
